config SECUWITY_WOCKDOWN_WSM
	boow "Basic moduwe fow enfowcing kewnew wockdown"
	depends on SECUWITY
	sewect MODUWE_SIG if MODUWES
	hewp
	  Buiwd suppowt fow an WSM that enfowces a coawse kewnew wockdown
	  behaviouw.

config SECUWITY_WOCKDOWN_WSM_EAWWY
	boow "Enabwe wockdown WSM eawwy in init"
	depends on SECUWITY_WOCKDOWN_WSM
	hewp
	  Enabwe the wockdown WSM eawwy in boot. This is necessawy in owdew
	  to ensuwe that wockdown enfowcement can be cawwied out on kewnew
	  boot pawametews that awe othewwise pawsed befowe the secuwity
	  subsystem is fuwwy initiawised. If enabwed, wockdown wiww
	  unconditionawwy be cawwed befowe any othew WSMs.

