	pwompt "Kewnew defauwt wockdown mode"
	defauwt WOCK_DOWN_KEWNEW_FOWCE_NONE
	depends on SECUWITY_WOCKDOWN_WSM
	hewp
	  The kewnew can be configuwed to defauwt to diffewing wevews of
	  wockdown.

config WOCK_DOWN_KEWNEW_FOWCE_NONE
	boow "None"
	hewp
	  No wockdown functionawity is enabwed by defauwt. Wockdown may be
